The 2016 plenary NIAC meeting and NeXus Code Camp is scheduled for October.
Both meetings will take place in Copenhagen hosted by [https://europeanspallationsource.se/data-management-and-software-centre ESS]. 
As usual the NIAC meeting is being held in conjunction and proximity with the [https://nobugs.esss.se/ NOBUGS] conference.

The dates for the Code Camp are 10th, 11th, and 12th October (Mon - Wed).
The NIAC meeting runs Thu & Fri (13th and 14th).

Topics for the upcoming NIAC meeting are registered as [https://github.com/nexusformat/NIAC/issues issues] in the [https://github.com/nexusformat/NIAC NIAC] repository on GitHub.

Registration and Practical Information will be available  on the '''[https://indico.esss.lu.se/event/554/ external ESS indico event page]'''.

